flowchart TD
    Start([Start Admin Session]) --> ViewPending[Get List of Pending Users]
    ViewPending --> SelectUser[Select User to Review]
    SelectUser --> InspectDocs[Inspect Uploaded NIC Images & Details]
    InspectDocs --> Decision{Decision: Approve or Reject?}
    
    Decision -- Approve --> CallApprove[Call POST /api/admin/approve/:id]
    CallApprove --> UpdateStatusApprove[Update Status to 'approved' & Clear Rejection Reason]
    UpdateStatusApprove --> AuditApprove[Log ADMIN_APPROVE_USER Action to Audit Log]
    AuditApprove --> NotifyApprove[Send SMS / System Notification: Account Activated]
    
    Decision -- Reject --> EnterReason[Provide Rejection Reason]
    EnterReason --> CallReject[Call POST /api/admin/reject/:id]
    CallReject --> UpdateStatusReject[Update Status to 'rejected' & Store Rejection Reason]
    UpdateStatusReject --> AuditReject[Log ADMIN_REJECT_USER Action to Audit Log]
    AuditReject --> NotifyReject[Send SMS / System Notification: Verification Rejected with Reason]
    
    NotifyApprove --> End([End])
    NotifyReject --> End
